00:13:46,607 --> 00:13:47,328
See you later.

294
00:13:49,088 --> 00:13:50,367
We can talk about it later.

295
00:13:50,367 --> 00:13:51,727
I'll meet an important client.

296
00:14:16,192 --> 00:14:17,247
(New Message: To Luo Yan)

297
00:14:17,247 --> 00:14:18,247
(I want to know)

298
00:14:18,247 --> 00:14:19,448
