301
00:14:42,727 --> 00:14:43,647
No.

302
00:14:44,288 --> 00:14:45,647
Auntie did it to protect me.

303
00:14:45,647 --> 00:14:46,527
I know that.

304
00:14:47,088 --> 00:14:48,688
I think she likes you quite a lot.

305
00:14:49,208 --> 00:14:51,688
Could you spend time
with her more often?

306
00:14:54,727 --> 00:14:55,688
Uh...

307
00:14:55,688 --> 00:14:56,328
Grandma,

308
00:14:56,568 --> 00:14:57,247
it's time for her

309
00:14:57,247 --> 00:14:58,808
to go back home.

310
00:14:59,007 --> 00:15:00,168
Go back home?

311
00:15:00,568 --> 00:15:02,088
This is Lili's home.

312
00:15:02,767 --> 00:15:04,487
The kiss Lili gave you just now

313
00:15:04,847 --> 00:15:06,487
