332
00:16:05,847 --> 00:16:07,288
After all, I've slept in it.

333
00:16:07,607 --> 00:16:08,607
I'll sleep

334
00:16:08,887 --> 00:16:09,887
on the couch.

335
00:16:12,208 --> 00:16:13,247
But, Mr. An,

336
00:16:16,688 --> 00:16:18,487
you've used this blanket, haven't you?

337
00:16:23,408 --> 00:16:24,887
Could you please get me a new one?

338
00:16:25,127 --> 00:16:25,887
Thank you.

339
00:16:26,288 --> 00:16:26,928
Fang Li,

340
00:16:26,928 --> 00:16:28,168
this is my home.

341
00:16:28,448 --> 00:16:30,568
You're bossing me around.

342
00:16:30,767 --> 00:16:32,647
Aren't you overstepping
your role as a guest?

343
00:16:33,048 --> 00:16:34,288
You have a problem?

344
00:16:35,607 --> 00:16:37,367
You can complain to your grandma.

345
00:16:37,847 --> 00:16:38,847
I guess

346
00:16:39,127 --> 00:16:41,247
Grandma wants you to chase after me.

347
00:16:43,607 --> 00:16:44,367
Okay.

348
00:16:44,847 --> 00:16:45,847
I'll get it

349
00:16:46,607 --> 00:16:49,127
as fulfilling the host's duties.

350
00:16:50,328 --> 00:16:51,328
You've got spine.

351
00:16:52,408 --> 00:16:53,328
Please hurry up.

352
00:16:58,887 --> 00:16:59,688
I warn you

353
00:16:59,847 --> 00:17:00,928
not to touch my things.

354
00:17:00,928 --> 00:17:02,367
After coming back, I will check.

355
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:34,688
(XIA SHANG INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL
DEVELOPMENT PLAN)

356
00:17:35,727 --> 00:17:37,968
He wants to build
an international school.

357
00:18:19,727 --> 00:18:20,688
