358
00:18:33,727 --> 00:18:35,928
If you want to sleep in the bed,
just say so.

359
00:18:35,928 --> 00:18:37,007
Why pretend to be asleep

360
00:18:37,007 --> 00:18:37,928
like a pig?

361
00:18:52,448 --> 00:18:53,487
You're like a pig.

362
00:18:58,784 --> 00:19:01,184
(Ju'an Group)

363
00:19:02,047 --> 00:19:03,487
This is An Yushen's plan.

364
00:19:03,727 --> 00:19:05,047
He bought Yin Zhiluo's land

365
00:19:05,047 --> 00:19:06,567
to cooperate with the school.

366
00:19:07,047 --> 00:19:08,168
If he really builds this

367
00:19:08,168 --> 00:19:09,567
international school,

368
00:19:09,727 --> 00:19:11,047
there will be better educational

369
00:19:11,047 --> 00:19:12,727
resources around the residential zone,

370
00:19:12,888 --> 00:19:14,727
and the price will also double.

371
00:19:17,087 --> 00:19:18,727
No wonder he spends 400 million yuan

372
00:19:18,968 --> 00:19:20,448
to secure this piece of land.

373
00:19:21,287 --> 00:19:23,208
It turns out he planned his next move.

374
00:19:24,487 --> 00:19:26,087
But if he hasn't signed the contract,

375
00:19:26,327 --> 00:19:28,327
I believe the school authorities
would not refuse

376
00:19:28,327 --> 00:19:29,888
a lower construction bid.

377
00:19:31,047 --> 00:19:32,287
You mean

378
00:19:33,007 --> 00:19:34,007
to intercept.

379
00:19:37,087 --> 00:19:39,247
An Yushen's finances
are already strained.

380
00:19:39,888 --> 00:19:41,888
So he won't offer a price too low.

381
00:19:43,047 --> 00:19:45,608
As long as we secure the school
at a lower price,

382
00:19:45,928 --> 00:19:48,007
we can thwart An Yushen's perfect plan.

383
00:19:48,688 --> 00:19:49,928
But our lowest cost price

384
00:19:49,928 --> 00:19:51,247
is 35 million yuan.

385
00:19:51,448 --> 00:19:52,448
The price

386
00:19:52,888 --> 00:19:54,767
cannot go below this figure.

387
00:19:56,767 --> 00:19:57,327
I got it.

388
00:19:59,208 --> 00:20:00,087
In that case,

389
00:20:00,247 --> 00:20:00,888
Principal Wei,

390
00:20:00,888 --> 00:20:01,888
let's settle on this.

391
00:20:01,888 --> 00:20:03,327
The land use rights are free.

392
00:20:03,408 --> 00:20:05,287
The total construction cost
is 50 million yuan,

393
00:20:05,408 --> 00:20:06,327
