394
00:20:14,408 --> 00:20:16,287
Principal Wei, don't rush your decision.

395
00:20:16,448 --> 00:20:18,247
You'd compare prices
even when buying clothes.

396
00:20:18,567 --> 00:20:20,448
Let alone constructing
such a large school.

397
00:20:20,807 --> 00:20:21,767
What are you doing here?

398
00:20:22,368 --> 00:20:23,767
We have an appointment with him,

399
00:20:24,448 --> 00:20:26,567
because we are also interested
in building school.

400
00:20:34,688 --> 00:20:35,208
Lili,

401
00:20:35,727 --> 00:20:36,888
