402
00:20:37,168 --> 00:20:38,247
You cannot always

403
00:20:38,247 --> 00:20:39,448
focus on others.

404
00:20:39,608 --> 00:20:40,408
Mr. An,

405
00:20:40,807 --> 00:20:42,327
business is won

406
00:20:42,327 --> 00:20:43,928
through competition.

407
00:20:44,368 --> 00:20:45,608
If you have the ability,

408
00:20:45,848 --> 00:20:47,408
you can also take on my project.

409
00:20:47,567 --> 00:20:49,287
We have land in the west of the city

410
00:20:49,287 --> 00:20:50,567
where we also build a school.

411
00:20:51,007 --> 00:20:52,888
Likewise, the land use rights are free.

412
00:20:53,247 --> 00:20:55,408
Mr. An is quite insincere

413
00:20:55,408 --> 00:20:57,168
with the 50 million yuan.

414
00:20:57,648 --> 00:21:00,007
Mr. Luo has always placed
great emphasis on education.

415
00:21:00,287 --> 00:21:01,807
He will offer you

416
00:21:01,807 --> 00:21:03,087
48 million yuan.

417
00:21:04,368 --> 00:21:06,767
I thought Mr. Luo had been generous.

418
00:21:07,287 --> 00:21:09,928
It turns out the dedication to education

419
00:21:09,928 --> 00:21:10,928
is no more than this.

420
00:21:12,007 --> 00:21:13,208
I'm willing to

421
00:21:13,448 --> 00:21:15,087
go down to 45 million yuan

422
00:21:15,767 --> 00:21:18,727
as a concession for arranging
nutrition for the students.

423
00:21:19,047 --> 00:21:20,448
Quibbling over every ounce

424
00:21:20,448 --> 00:21:22,168
is really your consistent style.

425
00:21:23,928 --> 00:21:24,727
Principal Wei,

426
00:21:24,727 --> 00:21:26,247
for the children,

427
00:21:26,928 --> 00:21:29,487
we'll offer 40 million yuan
to save you some budget

428
00:21:29,487 --> 00:21:31,168
to add sports facilities.

429
00:21:31,527 --> 00:21:33,648
It seems that Mr. Luo
is determined to succeed.

430
00:21:35,487 --> 00:21:36,527
I'm not for profit,

431
00:21:36,527 --> 00:21:37,567
but for charity.

432
00:21:39,527 --> 00:21:40,727
I'll offer 35 million yuan.

433
00:21:45,567 --> 00:21:46,327
30 million yuan.

434
00:21:48,408 --> 00:21:49,247
Mr. Luo.

435
00:21:54,608 --> 00:21:55,368
I concede.

436
00:21:56,408 --> 00:21:57,728
Wish you a pleasant cooperation.

437
00:22:03,208 --> 00:22:04,247
Well.

438
00:22:07,168 --> 00:22:08,408
Thanks to you this time,

439
00:22:08,408 --> 00:22:10,208
I was able to know
An Yushen's intentions.

440
00:22:10,767 --> 00:22:11,928
He can't turn losses

441
00:22:11,928 --> 00:22:12,727
into profits.

442
00:22:13,247 --> 00:22:14,648
But the price we offered

443
00:22:14,648 --> 00:22:15,888
is far below cost price,

444
00:22:15,888 --> 00:22:17,408
which means losing money.

445
00:22:19,047 --> 00:22:20,648
I don't mind taking a loss,

446
00:22:21,128 --> 00:22:22,408
as long as it can

447
00:22:23,087 --> 00:22:24,208
hurt my opponent.

448
00:22:51,476 --> 00:22:53,184
(Unknown Caller)

449
00:22:58,807 --> 00:22:59,888
Hello,

450
00:22:59,888 --> 00:23:00,968
who's speaking?

451
00:23:06,408 --> 00:23:07,487
It's you.

452
00:23:08,567 --> 00:23:09,727
It's really you.

453
00:23:13,287 --> 00:23:13,928
Mr. Luo.

454
00:23:18,567 --> 00:23:19,247
Mr. Luo.

455
00:23:19,448 --> 00:23:21,247
That's Secretary Lin's boyfriend.

456
00:23:24,648 --> 00:23:25,727
After so many years,

457
00:23:26,408 --> 00:23:27,327
you've grown taller.

458
00:23:27,688 --> 00:23:28,327
Not bad.

459
00:23:29,007 --> 00:23:29,527
Let's walk

460
00:23:29,527 --> 00:23:30,128
and talk.

461
00:23:30,128 --> 00:23:30,720
Okay.

462
00:23:36,928 --> 00:23:38,368
Am I driving today?

463
00:24:17,767 --> 00:24:19,087
Aside from the previous projects,

464
00:24:19,807 --> 00:24:20,727
yesterday, I just

465
00:24:20,727 --> 00:24:22,608
collaborated with
Xia Shang International School

466
00:24:23,128 --> 00:24:25,727
to develop their new campus
in the west side of the city.

467
00:24:26,767 --> 00:24:28,087
But as far as I know,

468
00:24:28,247 --> 00:24:30,727
your cooperation with
Xia Shang International School

469
00:24:30,727 --> 00:24:32,608
is a loss-making deal, right?

470
00:24:34,567 --> 00:24:35,487
Don't worry, Ms. Sun.

471
00:24:36,648 --> 00:24:38,287
My next plan is to

472
00:24:38,567 --> 00:24:39,888
develop residential areas

473
00:24:39,888 --> 00:24:41,727
and shopping malls around the school

474
00:24:42,047 --> 00:24:43,487
to create a high-end living circle.

475
00:24:43,688 --> 00:24:45,848
That will be a continuous profit chain.

476
00:24:49,888 --> 00:24:50,968
Mr. An,

477
00:24:50,968 --> 00:24:52,527
how is the project progressing?

478
00:24:53,327 --> 00:24:54,567
Share it with everyone please.

479
00:24:57,408 --> 00:24:58,688
Let's not talk

480
00:24:58,688 --> 00:25:00,087
about them today.

481
00:25:00,727 --> 00:25:02,007
You have to say something

482
00:25:02,608 --> 00:25:03,888
to make the directors know

483
00:25:04,567 --> 00:25:06,087
where they've spent

484
00:25:06,287 --> 00:25:07,368
the funds.

485
00:25:09,007 --> 00:25:09,968
Well, alright.

486
00:25:10,567 --> 00:25:11,968
If you want to listen,

487
00:25:12,208 --> 00:25:13,527
I'll just say a few words.

488
00:25:13,807 --> 00:25:16,287
I simply have reached a cooperation

489
00:25:16,527 --> 00:25:18,047
with a well-known

490
00:25:18,047 --> 00:25:19,848
amusement park operator, DX,

491
00:25:19,848 --> 00:25:21,368
to establish

492
00:25:21,567 --> 00:25:23,527
