499
00:25:37,848 --> 00:25:38,888
Upon completion,

500
00:25:38,888 --> 00:25:41,536
it's expected to yield annual profits
of over 500 million yuan.

501
00:25:42,608 --> 00:25:43,327
By the way,

502
00:25:43,848 --> 00:25:45,688
I also reached a cooperation

503
00:25:45,688 --> 00:25:47,287
with Xia Shang International School.

504
00:25:47,688 --> 00:25:50,408
The residents of my developed
residential buildings

505
00:25:50,567 --> 00:25:51,727
will also enjoy

506
00:25:51,727 --> 00:25:53,208
qualification admissions to it.

507
00:25:53,968 --> 00:25:54,567
You and...

508
00:26:18,047 --> 00:26:18,688
Mr. An,

509
00:26:18,968 --> 00:26:20,767
