523
00:26:46,527 --> 00:26:47,848
The file in your cabinet...

524
00:26:49,208 --> 00:26:51,848
Could it be that you didn't

525
00:26:51,848 --> 00:26:53,287
listen to me and rummaged

526
00:26:53,807 --> 00:26:54,888
through my things?

